package presentation
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    BackgroundMusic
    The BackgroundMusic class manages the background music and sound effects for the game.
    ChooseNumberOfPlayers
    The ChooseNumberOfPlayers class represents the menu for choosing the number of players in the Quoridor game application.
    CreatePlayers
    The CreatePlayers class represents the menu for creating players in the Quoridor game application.
    GameTurn
    The GameTurn class represents a game in the game application.
    HandleMovePawn
    Handles the movement of pawns in the game.
    HandlePlaceWall
    Handles the placement of walls in the game.
    LoadGame
    The LoadGame class represents a JavaFX application for loading a saved game.
    Menu
    The Menu class represents the main menu of the Quoridor game application.
    Rules
    The Rules class represents the rules menu of the Quoridor game application.
    SaveGame
    The SaveGame class represents a JavaFX application for saving a game.
